        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Restoring Health Benefits for Justice-Involved Individuals Act of 2019</strong></p> <p>This bill allows an otherwise eligible individual who&nbsp;is in custody pending disposition of charges (i.e., pretrial detainees) to receive Medicare, Children's Health Insurance Program (CHIP), or veterans' health benefits.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
